To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private TimeProfile _tp;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_tp = TP(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_tp.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "volumeperprice", _tp.VolumePerPrice.Current.Value);
    Plot("My Indicators", "profilehigh", _tp.ProfileHigh.Current.Value);
    Plot("My Indicators", "profilelow", _tp.ProfileLow.Current.Value);
    Plot("My Indicators", "pocprice", _tp.POCPrice.Current.Value);
    Plot("My Indicators", "pocvolume", _tp.POCVolume.Current.Value);
    Plot("My Indicators", "valueareavolume", _tp.ValueAreaVolume.Current.Value);
    Plot("My Indicators", "valueareahigh", _tp.ValueAreaHigh.Current.Value);
    Plot("My Indicators", "valuearealow", _tp.ValueAreaLow.Current.Value);
    Plot("My Indicators", "timeprofile", _tp.Current.Value);
}
